      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the tip. i'm a bit worried about the roots though, they look kind of tangled and messy in there. is there anything specific i should look for when i'm cleaning them up or checking if they're healthy? like how do i know if they're actually okay or if they're rotton?",
      "source": "evaluator"
